data.title: Schwerin at the coronation of Nicholas II, Emperor of Russia
data.meta_description: Photogravure of the representatives of the Grand Duchy of Mecklenburg-Schwerin present at the coronation of Nicholas II, Emperor of Russia. There are nine men standing in a row, all wearing ceremonial military uniform. Frederick Francis III, Grand Duke of Mecklenburg-Schwerin (1851-97) is standing third from the right. His wife Grand Duchess Anastasia of Mecklenburg-Schwerin (1860-1922) is sitting beside him and Mrs Maltzhan is sitting to the far left. There are plants behind them and a patterned rug on...
